{"tid":2130232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】金鐘太古廣場有人中招 無良共享辦公室為左錢唔理員工生死","createTime":"2020-07-29T06:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T04:29:20.000Z","uid":221844,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d2b5dd5c055fb6905f43df49fa961b7970c068","tid":2130232,"uid":221844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:02:31.000Z","msg":"[代frd開post]<br />\n<br />\n金鐘太古廣場二期一間共享辦公室有確診個案 但係公司無即時關閉淨係收左工先消毒 仲要求員工向客人隱瞞病情同繼續返工<br />\n<br />\n無得WFH已經係其次 重要繼續返係叫其他centre既同事去確診centre返工 打份工姐洗唔洗賣命啊 千祈唔好入呢問仆街公司做 慘過做狗 用生命值硬接<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVaomSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVaomSQ.jpg&h=c33ba381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話唔好disclose to members姐 可以disclose比大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求各位絲打巴打幫我share開去 金鐘太古廣場好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">各位睇路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c3f444539f011fa22a57b412956d9400fc3c51","tid":2130232,"uid":70771,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"冇頭冇尾既email係人都作到出黎<br />\n有冇多d證據"},{"pid":"08712b31ffd79f4223561bf3fee43e778bba1aa5","tid":2130232,"uid":127929,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n填充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfd8747d62f4f48f661e1756729a28bbfaddd83","tid":2130232,"uid":45320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:05:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2697c53c9f6af612263beb58d61c56c478b292d3","tid":2130232,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"244412c8ae7ff033a30c463891535fef01216e58","tid"